mical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WH9v2sgW%2FSpX0dt9kAViQ4CQvjwpbchu9ZJulaRarZqKDvYAszEevxk7hO22n33PzNhggqMiof0nIvbMuef%2BvtdfDkI%2BYVmUvpEhPzg9ODqis7MzulNMxJRKChT7c4kfi5jus7bnH9NCqih8FHxBC3%2FUHnVHvVF%2F5HdHfp9qOpUJ%2Bf26wbiPgXWudTZPUiFjCmaAPCWPEqZkMBMsMoj%2BoE0%2BTZgasQVbjmbZnMW6eNEmFos5i%2FRIyzlfzFhavOnSJEszxfMLozlLU65GC5HORqHQgcziVMTT4niPYll%2BPtq4XZzqr8TlcGwUyZVIv0s6YQEf8acEl6DSaMyCh4lQfIUAGyRcabxikwkPrChjKmuLIQtmxNYGEZoYvV%2BmM%2FyeiIgTLL5%2BrY8oNQqzMNQNUhxuEjEkSWXBFG%2FCjmzOwVNoPE9n3Jn43xq2iQOL8YoCOU%2BkNqZYHcDdOORAxCOhLZpOWRyySMac5oiDqEWfV24ePn42VM11aA6lcPGRRRknObEI64hoWbDXXKc0zpaUGTHmouZlxU7pdqbEPKHfeATHc3qv5B%2FAdbd%2FHr4b3pzfDS9ovKQpj7liKW8lyyL8eCjSDTMd4mUD%2Fk0dGWNJIFmsD3HAVWpUnkuFeFtZTLuzzhwsSSLBdYtul%2FNWJKexVAiC2pek26Bk0P1at1jWWwPvB3rz9pU9OeYpc08TJcdsLCKRgshYGrVDkzsfvQb5n1p0yYJUQiZ0dVA4kBgfxGmDtCRuAkOqKTw3%2FLi4OL%2F6%2Fehfn2jMI7lAZpi71sP8Cb%2BjJa4DG1a1WJAdZkHqfAHvcYQm1HfxfZFHPJ0hx8icxsNmKuacfqKApUynSia4ZsI9zpgNSxONTDUdQu7p2g2ba748uoXtYvrm%2FXC0VPSo6Z1U4Yxlmr75ra55%2BAqCzuAMKpINxrNZ8zpPlWuUGmHsrXBuy%2BAoDy2vbc1ufva%2B1i3tFOFieG3EYE5wMTOpw5mCZVaZadKDqbmL2hn7k6mQahc8C2O%2BhJXDjEXNzEYlFJIiPJJqLFJEiIgnylgFJgX4K4Qokk7pOeqKNgxm1iUK5p5ABi5oxHBTZ5OJCASPA3hHQ%2BUENQHefc9lEvFLxWw2Vivc4U2vv9LY87xOrrSemdyAX9kjgpiHzbLDnFtYEKjM5rZE3TGyYA7E05NABrJ4iYp6St863PcpZ0SRmPDmEu