nt soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+15+17+18]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;   21k lives-eq/$1k · 72% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Wild insects (humane pesticides) · 28%&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + space_expansion_backfires + person_affecting_view + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 17 person_affecting_view → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WGtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6unbEdyY5f6WaBtHFmik07RZKiGDSFS0u0zYksakkpjqfT%2FvY9JCVbjl1UgDEfYigSee65T97LL0chn7IsSl%2FJkB%2BdHZ2c0Pn5Od0pJmJKJQWK%2FbnCwzKm%2B6zt%2Bae0lCoKHwVf0tIft8fdcW%2FcH%2FvdsY%2FfAdV0KhPyB3UDcx8D7kLrbJGkQsYUzIF6Rh4lTMlgLlhkQP1hm3yaMjVmS7Yaz7MFi3XxoU0sFgsW6bGWC76cs7T40qVplmaK5xvGC5amXI2XIp2PQ6EDmcWpiGfF8h7Fsvx%2BvLW7WNVfi8vh2DiSa5F%2Bl3TCAj7mTwk2QaXxhAUPU6H4GsHvU8KVxic2nfLAirLWKr4PSEsRjXM51kQjFsyJbewkNDF6t0rneJ6KiBN8sfmsTyg1dmBhqBukOBwoYhCQyoIp3oR52YKDvtB4n865s%2Fy%2FNEwWBxbjBQVykUhtLLRegL1xyIGIV8JR0ymLQxbJmNMCERK16PM6AEaPnw1Vsx0Gga7Y%2BMiijJOcWoRNrLQs2EuuU5pkK8qMGLNR87JiZ3Q7V2KR0AceIR44vVPyD%2BC63b%2BM3o5uLu5GlzRZ0YzHXLGUt5JVEZg8FOmWmY7xsQG3p46MsSSQLNb7OOAqNSovpEIYri2m3VpnDpYkkeC6RberRSuSs1gq%2BKz2Jek2KBl2v9YtlvXW0PuJXr1%2BYVdOeMrc20TJCZuISK